                                <p rend="center">[Daily Bulletin, August 2, 1889.]</p>
                                <p rend="center"><hi rend="smallcaps">killed, revolution of</hi>
                                    1889.</p>
                                <p>Loika, Poni, Sam Tucker, Keki, Kelelua, Kawaiwai, Tom Kapa. Total
